item.title: Dan Winstanley
item.description: Technical Lead Web: https://winstanley.au Email: dan@winstanley.au Hi, and thanks for the interest! Given the open nature of the internet, I’ve opted not to publish my full CV here. However, if you’re considering my skills for a project or consulting work, feel free to reach out and I’ll be more than happy to provide. For a snapshot of my recent work and a condensed work history, you’re welcome to visit my LinkedIn profile.
